      <event start="T134" end="T318-165">ne. </event>
      <event start="T318-165" end="T135">Mi pa smo malo lehko bole luft bremzali, </event>
      <event start="T135" end="T136">ne, </event>
      <event start="T136" end="T137">tak ka smo ... bli bole na b() b() na igrišči, na ulici v bistvi na, </event>
      <event start="T137" end="T326-817">po šumah se lovili. </event>
      <event start="T326-817" end="T510">To na kmetijah je, tega ni tejko blo, </event>
