      <event start="T960-244" end="T431">Eee ... </event>
      <event start="T431" end="T532">tako bi rekel, ka so bolj, </event>
      <event start="T532" end="T432">to kaj smo imeli iste letnice, </event>
      <event start="T432" end="T433">smo nekako, </event>
      <event start="T433" end="T966-045">ne, </event>
      <event start="T966-045" end="T434">ni, </event>
      <event start="T434" end="T435">ne, </event>
      <event start="T435" end="T533">so rajši starejše gledale, </event>
      <event start="T533" end="T436">ki smo bili mladi še bolj takšni mlečni pa sramežljivi, </event>
      <event start="T436" end="T972-857">ne. </event>
      <event start="T972-857" end="T438">Mmm ja, </event>
      <event start="T438" end="T437">to smo te kak sss, </event>
      <event start="T437" end="T439">smo se kje dobili </event>
      <event start="T439" end="T978-357">pa smo šli kakšni sladoled pa ... </event>
      <event start="T978-357" end="T440">Kaj vem, </event>
      <event start="T440" end="T441">smo se kje vkup špilali </event>
      <event start="T441" end="T981-471">pa hecali pa ... </event>
      <event start="T981-471" end="T982-656">Tako je bilo. </event>
      <event start="T985-037" end="T442">Jah, </event>
      <event start="T442" end="T443">tudi, </event>
      <event start="T443" end="T986-033">ja. </event>
      <event start="T986-823" end="T444">Ja ja, </event>
      <event start="T444" end="T987-742">tudi. </event>
      <event start="T987-742" end="T989-716">Eee tudi, ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T995-695" end="T996-962">Aja. </event>
      <event start="T996-962" end="T998-385">Eee s polži. </event>
      <event start="T999-444" end="T1000-045">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1000-045" end="T445">Tu gori pri šoli so eni eee polže kupovali, </event>
      <event start="T445" end="T1003-491">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1003-491" end="T446">Eee no pa te se so, seveda, te si z() ... [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T446" end="T1009-722">Več jih je bilo te, da je bilo malo ... eee dežja, </event>
      <event start="T1009-722" end="T1010-465">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1010-465" end="T448">Te pa si šel pa z() po koprivah, </event>
      <event start="T448" end="T449">si tu s() pobral polže, </event>
      <event start="T449" end="T450">pa si te kilo, dve, si takoj nabral, </event>
      <event start="T450" end="T1022-347">pa si to toliko te dobil, ka si ... imel za kino pa za za za ... sladoled kakšni, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1023-545" end="T1024-481">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1024-481" end="T451">Pa za kakšni sladoled, </event>
      <event start="T451" end="T452">to je bilo, </event>
      <event start="T452" end="T1026-741">ja. </event>
      <event start="T1026-741" end="T453">No, </event>
      <event start="T453" end="T454">samo te ni, </event>
      <event start="T454" end="T455">ne, </event>
      <event start="T455" end="T1030-216">te smo še bili malo mlajši. </event>
      <event start="T1030-216" end="T456">Te ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T456" end="T457">mislim, ka to bilo v osnovni šoli, </event>
      <event start="T457" end="T1033-504">te smo še ne to tako. </event>
      <event start="T1034-373" end="T1035-369">Ne ne ne. </event>
      <event start="T1039-352" end="T1040-948">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1040-948" end="T459">Eee </event>
      <event start="T459" end="T1045-848">mislim, ka je tu bil prvi [zvok] ... moto zbor, </event>
      <event start="T1045-848" end="T1051-565">to pa je bilo, eee leta leta tisoč devetsto dvaindevetdeset ali pa triindevetdeset. </event>
      <event start="T1051-565" end="T1052-814">Nekje tam je bilo. </event>
      <event start="T1053-318" end="T458">Tu še eden eee z Desnjaka tu organizira, </event>
      <event start="T458" end="T1057-033">tu pri Gajševcih. </event>
      <event start="T1057-033" end="T460">Prvi moto zbor je bil, </event>
      <event start="T460" end="T1058-566">ja. </event>
      <event start="T1058-566" end="T1060-226">Te pa ... </event>
      <event start="T1060-226" end="T461">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T461" end="T462">so, </event>
      <event start="T462" end="T463">zdaj je že več skupin. </event>
      <event start="T463" end="T465">Samo tota, </event>
      <event start="T465" end="T464">to so bili toro(), </event>
      <event start="T464" end="T1066-375">to so bili toti motoristi Road Warriorsi, </event>
      <event start="T1066-375" end="T534">eee ki so organizirali, </event>
      <event start="T534" end="T466">pa so bili zelo skeptični, </event>
      <event start="T466" end="T467">so mislili, ka to ne+bo šlo, </event>
      <event start="T467" end="T468">ne, </event>
      <event start="T468" end="T469">in to je pjo() to je tako folka prišlo, ka so, </event>
      <event start="T469" end="T470">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T470" end="T1079-937">ka so oni še celo zmenili, ka so ponoči s Pivovarne Laško tovornjak piva pripeljali. </event>
      <event start="T1079-937" end="T471">V ... to so pipe, </event>
      <event start="T471" end="T472">osem pip je bilo, </event>
      <event start="T472" end="T473">pa so to na pipe, </event>
      <event start="T473" end="T474">osem fasnov, </event>
      <event start="T474" end="T475">to je v potokih, </event>
      <event start="T475" end="T476">ne, </event>
      <event start="T476" end="T1087-705">ne vem, koliko tisoč ljudi je bilo. </event>
      <event start="T1087-705" end="T478">To so nekaj neverjetnega, </event>
      <event start="T478" end="T479">niso pričakovali, ka da takšne, </event>
      <event start="T479" end="T1092-7">ne, eee </event>
      <event start="T1092-7" end="T1094-138">toliko motoristov priš(). </event>
      <event start="T1095-845" end="T1096-962">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T1096-962" end="T480">kar po dosti stvareh, </event>
      <event start="T480" end="T1098-184">ja. </event>
      <event start="T1100-081" end="T481">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T481" end="T482">Prvi filmski zapis, eee konjske dirke, eee vina, eee slo() prvi slovenski tabo(), prvi slovenski tabor, </event>
      <event start="T482" end="T1108-237">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1109-549" end="T1110-868">Prleški s(). </event>
      <event start="T1110-868" end="T483">Grossman, </event>
      <event start="T483" end="T1111-953">ja. </event>
      <event start="T1124-052" end="T485">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T485" end="T486">težko pitanje, </event>
      <event start="T486" end="T1126-284">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1126-284" end="T487">Pa verjetno ne, </event>
      <event start="T487" end="T1128-513">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1128-513" end="T490">K se(), ja, </event>
      <event start="T490" end="T488">sem imel kar lepo, </event>
      <event start="T488" end="T489">lepo otroštvo sem imel, </event>
      <event start="T489" end="T1132-465">ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T1132-465" end="T1135-065">Ni nam nič falilo. </event>
      <event start="T1135-065" end="T1136-013">Ne, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1136-013" end="T491">Saj smo si ne mislili, ka mi kaj slabo živimo, </event>
      <event start="T491" end="T492">ne, </event>
      <event start="T492" end="T493">saj tako, tako je bilo, </event>
      <event start="T493" end="T494">ne, </event>
      <event start="T494" end="T1143-063">tako se, mmm nihče ni mislil, ka on zdaj pa ni [nerazumljivo]. </event>
      <event start="T1143-063" end="T495">Penez je tako nihče ni imel, </event>
      <event start="T495" end="T496">ne, </event>
      <event start="T496" end="T1146-272">če si kaj imel, si te ... </event>
      <event start="T1146-272" end="T498">Samo nismo se zzz </event>
      <event start="T498" end="T499">lepo smo živeli, </event>
      <event start="T499" end="T500">ne, </event>
      <event start="T500" end="T501">nisem tako ka bi zdaj rekel: </event>
      <event start="T501" end="T502">"U, </event>
      <event start="T502" end="T1150-554">zdaj pa ima ovi to." </event>
      <event start="T1150-554" end="T1153-337">Zdaj so dosti večje razlike, kak so nekdaj bile, ne. </event>
      <event start="T1154-112" end="T1154-732">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1154-732" end="T503">Nekdaj ni bilo to takšnih groznih razlik, </event>
      <event start="T503" end="T1157-257">ne. </event>
      <event start="T1157-257" end="T1160-125">Eee. [zvok] </event>
    </tier>
